text: Karen Noelia Vénica (born 25 January 1992) is an Argentine footballer who plays as a midfielder for UAI Urquiza. She was a member of the Argentina women's national team. She appeared at the 2014 Copa América Femenina and the 2015 Pan American Games. ==Personal life== Vénica is a supporter of River Plate. ==References== Category:1992 births Category:Living people Category:People from General Obligado Department Category:Sportspeople from Santa Fe Province Category:Argentine women's footballers Category:Women's association football midfielders Category:UAI Urquiza (women) players Category:Argentina women's international footballers Category:Footballers at the 2015 Pan American Games Category:Pan American Games competitors for Argentina
